description: Launched on 15/01/2019 by Currency.com team based in Gibraltar and Belarus, represents a tokenised version of traditional financial market - Health Care Select Sector SPDR Fund shares on Ethereum blockchain, price of underlined assets is tailored to Health Care Select Sector SPDR Fund market price. Tokenisation of the asset provides possibility to invest to popular financial markets worldwide using crypto.
name: Health Care Select Sector SPDR Fund
